  "content": "<p data-pid=\"jqAJdlvn\">有点像 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//sivers.org/nowff\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">/now page</a>，但时间范围更广，而且专注于我所想的事情。</p><ul><li data-pid=\"4G7J8Qeq\"> 通过 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z72ioKyd4X48WndtAsfkhnKwsD8o5PaaT384o\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Orbit</a> 扩展和理解<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z4rRX3qwSSJRsEkdXKwH2shamgHNeRthrMLiF\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">助记媒介</a><sup data-text=\"助记媒介（Mnemonic medium）\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/459483765\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"vozwqLJO\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z3SjnvsB5aR2ddsycyXofbYR7fCxo7RmKW2be\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">常青笔记写作是知识工作的基本单位</a><sup data-text=\"常青笔记写作是知识工作的基本单位\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/428784607\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup><br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"5iku586_\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z5ARNXtS5VxteskEW91S1yYTgAcLABNXsZuJE\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">助记媒介可以扩展到个人笔记上</a><sup data-text=\"助记媒介可以扩展到个人笔记上\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/487321909\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup><br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"BrkxKCKs\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z244xx3kMf1v8UnkZKUwQBAwBsHLpUgN4YhsG\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">§赋能环境、游戏和 the Primer</a> / <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z6oXuXLZ7Wq1